PNB TO SELL $ 200 MILLION CONVERTIBLE BONDS . Philippine National Bank ( PNB ) said on Thursday its board approved the issuance of convertible bonds in the amount of $ 200 million . The PNB statement did not give any details of the offering . PNB is one of the largest banks in the country . - - Manila Newsroom 63 2 841 - 8937 fax 8176267 - - Email : manila . newsroom @ reuters . com 
